name: sherman1
description:
Unfolding of a sherman1 sparse matrix into a lattice. The original matrix describes a computational fluid dynamics problem first documented by A. Sherman in 1984. In this simulation, the matrix is represented as a lattice with 1000 nodes which undergoes a process of unfolding until it reaches equilibrium. 

@lukapiskorec, mp4, 1000 x 1000 pix, 300 frames
